 Malone 和 Florence + The Machine 合作</a>。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_91 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_91" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-the-official-tracklist-for-taylor-swifts-the-tortured-poets-department-3583090"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>在格莱美奖的其他地方，泰勒·斯威夫特凭借《Midnights》荣获年度专辑奖，这是她第四次获得该奖项。凭借这一胜利，斯威夫特现在成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-wins-record-setting-fourth-album-of-the-year-at-2024-grammys-3582336">年度最佳专辑奖项的历史领先者，创下了新纪录</a>。她此前与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-wonder">史蒂夫·旺德</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-simon">保罗·西蒙</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-sinatra">弗兰克·西纳特拉</a>并列三场胜利。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swift-dear-reader-live-debut-japan-3584261">《观看泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 为《亲爱的读者》(Dear Reader) 在日本举行的现场首演》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
