ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/nick-cave-warren-ellis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/nick-cave-warren-ellis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/nick-cave-warren-ellis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯</a>传记片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/watch-the-first-official-teaser-for-amy-winehouse-biopic-back-to-black-3569022"><em>《Back To Black》</em></a>已确认由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warren-ellis">沃伦·埃利斯</a>创作音乐。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/features/amy-winehouse-anniversary-tribute-the-zutons-valerie-dionne-bromfield-2998396"><b>艾米怀恩豪斯的永恒影响：“她的遗产是无法理解的”</b></a></li></ul><p>根据 Canal 工作室的一份新闻稿，电影导演萨姆·泰勒-约翰逊邀请凯夫和埃利斯为这部电影配乐，并表示他们是她心目中“唯一为<em>《背靠背》</em>配乐的音乐家”。</p><p>泰勒-约翰逊在一份声明中表示：“多年来，我聆听了他们创作的所有作品，并渴望实现合作的梦想。他们对这个故事的敏感度和理解造就了深刻而感人的电影配乐。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3DbhTCIdNo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px;